languages.text: "Рядом с тобой моей душе неспокойно, Зрящая Ша'эиль. Дело в твоем третьем оке? Или есть что-то еще?.. В любом случае — не стоит подходить ближе".
"You make my soul uneasy, seer of Sha'eil. Is it your third eye? Or is it something else? Whatever it is, do not come any closer."

languages.text: “纱芮尔的先知，你让我的灵魂躁动不安。那就是你的第三只眼吗？还是别的什么东西？不管是什么，都不要再靠近我了。”
languages.original_text: "You make my soul uneasy, seer of Sha'eil. Is it your third eye? Or is it something else? Whatever it is, do not come any closer."

traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: « Vous perturbez mon âme, divinatrice du Sha'eil. Serait-ce à cause de votre troisième œil ? Ou d'autre chose ? Je l'ignore. Quoi qu'il en soit, n'approchez pas davantage. »
languages.original_text: "You make my soul uneasy, seer of Sha'eil. Is it your third eye? Or is it something else? Whatever it is, do not come any closer."

traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "Ihr macht meine Seele unruhig, Seherin von Sha'eil. Liegt das an Eurem dritten Auge? Oder an etwas anderem? Was es auch ist, kommt keinen Schritt näher."

languages.text: 「あなたは私の魂を不安にさせる、シャーエイルの予見者よ。第三の目？それとも他の何かか？何であれ、これ以上近づかないで」
languages.original_text: "You make my soul uneasy, seer of Sha'eil. Is it your third eye? Or is it something else? Whatever it is, do not come any closer."

languages.text: «Haces que mi alma se inquiete, vidente del Sha'eil. ¿Es por tu tercer ojo? ¿O hay otro motivo? Sea lo que sea, no te acerques más».
languages.original_text: "You make my soul uneasy, seer of Sha'eil. Is it your third eye? Or is it something else? Whatever it is, do not come any closer."
